  Version bump to the theme from the 2006.1 release.

*splash-themes-livecd-2006.0 (16 Mar 2006)

  16 Mar 2006; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org>
  +splash-themes-livecd-2006.0.ebuild:
  Added 2006.0 splash theme. I am committing this straight to stable since it
  was used by these architectures for the release and is known to work
  properly. Plus, it really should have been added before the release, and I
  simply forgot about it.

  08 Feb 2006; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org>
  splash-themes-livecd-2005.1.ebuild:
  Added sed from blackace and closing bug #121559.

  23 Jul 2005; Lars Weiler <pylon@gentoo.org>
  splash-themes-livecd-2005.1.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc.

